            Your resume never leaves your device. Only semantic vectors are uploaded.<br/>
            Even if we get hacked, attackers only get meaningless numbers.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
            <h3>Zero PII Storage</h3>
            <p>We store only 1536-dimensional vectors, not your personal information. Mathematical guarantee against data reconstruction.</p>
            <a href="/privacy-proof" class="feature-link">See the proof →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
            <h3>87% Cost Savings</h3>
            <p>Vectors are 87% smaller than full text. Lower storage costs, reduced GDPR compliance burden.</p>
            <a href="/privacy-proof" class="feature-link">Calculate savings →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
            <h3>Semantic Search</h3>
            <p>Find perfect matches using meaning, not keywords. Natural language queries powered by OpenAI embeddings.</p>
            <a href="/search" class="feature-link">Try searching →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
            <h3>Client-Side Embedding</h3>
            <p>Generate vectors in your browser. Your resume text never touches our servers.</p>
            <a href="/upload-resume" class="feature-link">See how it works →</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="demo-section">
        <h2>Interactive Demos</h2>
        <div class="demo-cards">
            <div class="demo-card">
