            </div>

            <div class="demo-card">
                <h3>🔍 Company Search</h3>
                <p>Experience privacy-protected search from a recruiter's perspective. See how profile IDs protect candidate identity.</p>
                <a href="/search" class="btn btn-primary">Try Search Demo</a>
            </div>

            <div class="demo-card">
                <h3>🛡️ Privacy & Cost Proof</h3>
                <p>Interactive proof of security and cost benefits. Simulate a data breach and see what attackers actually get.</p>
                <a href="/privacy-proof" class="btn btn-primary">View Proof</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="how-it-works-section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h4>Enter Resume</h4>
                <p>Type or paste your resume in the browser</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h4>Generate Vector</h4>
                <p>OpenAI creates 1536-dim embedding locally</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h4>Upload Vector Only</h4>
                <p>Numbers sent to server, text stays with you</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <h4>Semantic Matching</h4>
                <p>Companies find you by skills, not keywords</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-highlight">
        <div class="comparison-side traditional-side">
            <h3>❌ Traditional Job Boards</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Store full resume text</li>
                <li>High data breach risk</li>
                <li>Complex GDPR compliance</li>
                <li>$2,623/month storage cost</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="vs-divider">VS</div>
        <div class="comparison-side privatematch-side">
            <h3>✅ PrivateMatch</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Store only vectors (numbers)</li>
                <li>Zero breach risk</li>
                <li>Minimal compliance burden</li>
                <li>$208/month storage cost</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-stack-section">
