            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
                <strong>Azure Functions</strong>
                <p>.NET 8.0 isolated worker model</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
                <strong>Cosmos DB</strong>
                <p>Serverless vector storage</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
                <strong>Blazor WebAssembly</strong>
                <p>Client-side C# in browser</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>Experience Privacy-First Matching</h2>
